OL,4,G0855FFind It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,5,     GSimon O'Brien's restorer Gemma
OL,6,     Gturns an old TV cabinet into a
OL,7,     Gluxury dog bed, while Henry Cole
OL,8,     Gtrades in his lifelong love of
OL,9,     Gmechanicals to upcycle wooden
OL,10,     Gfurniture.
OL,11,G0955FFind It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,12,     GIn Oxford, Henry and Simon
OL,13,     Gexplore a second-hand shop,
OL,14,     Gfinding a call bell and strange
OL,15,     Gtool.
OL,16,G1055FFour in a Bed
OL,17,     GThe week kicks off at the
OL,18,     GJuniperlea Inn in Midlothian,
OL,19,     Gwhere host Carly aims to wow her
OL,20,     Grivals with her stylish decor.
OL,21,     GBut one guest certainly isn't
OL,22,     Gwowed by the roadside location.
